Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 01 of Head MRI

When I select 'Seizure' from 'Indication' dropdown menu
Then 'Add indication' button is enabled
And 'Suspected' radio button is enabled
And 'Exclusion' radio button is enabled
And 'Follow-up examination' radio button is enabled
And 'Known epilepsy' radio button is enabled
And 'First seizure' radio button is enabled
And 'Status epilepticus' radio button is enabled
And 'Refractory epilepsy' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'First seizure' radio button
Then 'Month' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Year' dropdown menu is enabled
